title: Clickflow
longDescription:
ClickFlow is SEO and business intelligence software that helps you grow your SEO traffic through SEO A/B testing.

ClickFlow will allow you to:
- Run single page title and meta description tests to increase your traffic - Track each and every tests that youâ€™ve ran automatically to save you time - Run group tests on entire categories (for larger websites) - Run reports to validate your work - See the top 50 keywords per page and traffic, ranking, CTR and impression numbers
